Sentencas: We investigated the electrochemical properties of Co-Fe perovskites, which can be used as cathodes for intermediate-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Performance of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-yFeyO3 (y=0.2, 0.5 and 0.8) nanostructured cathodes for intermediate-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells: Influence of microstructure and composition

Sentencas: We studied the electrochemical properties of nanostructured mixed ionic-electronic conductors for IT-SOFC cathodes with compositions of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-yFeyO3 (y=0.2, 0.5 and 0.8).
Titulo: Performance of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-yFeyO3 (y=0.2, 0.5 and 0.8) nanostructured cathodes for intermediate-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells: Influence of microstructure and composition

Sentencas: We analyzed the performance of two types of nanostructures: nanorods and nanotubes.
Titulo: Performance of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-yFeyO3 (y=0.2, 0.5 and 0.8) nanostructured cathodes for intermediate-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells: Influence of microstructure and composition

Sentencas: Our results show that the electrochemical performance is highly influenced by the form of nanostructure, whereas the effect of composition is less significant.
Titulo: Performance of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-yFeyO3 (y=0.2, 0.5 and 0.8) nanostructured cathodes for intermediate-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells: Influence of microstructure and composition
